The paper deals with image restoration, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of Robust Principal Component Analysis (RPCA) and quasiconformal maps suggests that the paper may also belong to the sub-categories of graphics (cs.GR) and information theory (cs.IT). Additionally, the paper involves image processing techniques such as deblurring and fusion, which are relevant to multimedia (cs.MM) and signal processing (cs.SD).
